A student is given the function $f\left(x\right)$ defined as follows:

\begin{eqnarray}
f\left(x\right) &=& \begin{cases} 
\sqrt[3]{x}\cos{\left(x^2\right)}, & \mbox{if } x \neq 0 \notag \\
0, & \mbox{if } x = 0 \notag
\end{cases}
\end{eqnarray}

