\section{Bitcoin~\label{sct::bitcoin}} In this section we analyze the security of Bitcoin's~\cite{satoshi:bitcoin} proof-of-work protocol, which is based on finding a hash\footnote{The hash function being used by the protocol is H($x$) := SHA-256(SHA-256($x$).} pre-image which that starts
